{
    "name": "升级",
    "icon": "productivebees:upgrade_base",
    "category": "productivebees:items",
    "pages": [
        {
            "type": "spotlight",
            "item": "productivebees:upgrade_base",
            "text": "升级可以放入机器或蜂箱来加强它们的功能或改善外观。"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/base",
            "text": "所有其它升级的基础。"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/breeding",
            "text": "可用：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩展蜂箱$(/l)、$(l:blocks/catcher)捕捉器$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "babee"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "当安装在一个蜂箱时，繁殖升级会给与蜂箱内蜜蜂一个微小的无需你参与的繁殖并产生后代的几率。$(br)当安装在一个$(l:blocks/catcher)捕捉器$(/l)时，只有小蜜蜂会被捕捉并放入笼中。"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/productivity",
            "text": "可用：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩展蜂箱$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "productivity"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "当安装在一个蜂箱时，产量升级将增加蜜蜂每次旅行生产蜜脾的数量。可安装多种生产升级。"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/time",
            "text": "可用：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩展蜂箱$(/l)、$(l:blocks/centrifuge)离心机$(/l)、$(l:blocks/incubator)小蜜蜂孵化器$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "speed"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "当安装在一个蜂箱时，速度升级会减低蜜蜂在蜂箱内消耗的时间。$(br)当安装在一个$(l:blocks/centrifuge)离心机$(/l)或一个$(l:blocks/incubator)小蜜蜂孵化器$(/l)时，它会减少增加运行速度。"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/filter",
            "text": "可用：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩展蜂箱$(/l)、$(l:blocks/catcher)捕捉器$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "filter"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "右键一个蜜蜂将其添加到过滤器。将过滤器放在合成格上来清除它。当安装在一个蜂箱时，只有在过滤器中指定的蜜蜂可以进入。$(br)当安装在一个捕捉器时，只有在过滤器中指定的蜜蜂可以被捕捉。"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/range",
            "text": "可用：$(l:blocks/catcher)捕捉器$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "range"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "当安装在一个捕捉器时，范围升级将在所有方向扩展一格操作范围。可以安装多个范围升级。"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/anti_teleport",
            "text": "可用：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩展蜂箱$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "anti_teleport"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "当安装在一个蜂箱时，可传送的蜜蜂将无法传送。"
        },
        {
            "type": "crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/bee_sampler",
            "text": "可用：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩展蜂箱$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "sampler"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "当安装在一个蜂箱时，每次蜜蜂访问将提取一小份蜂蜜授粉样本。这不会伤害它们。"
        }
    ]
}